{
  "stem": "26609.12",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember I had a-- a green coat, and in the pocket, I kept the birth certificate which the Pole, Polish woman gave me, with my name as Wanda Grabowienska.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was it, in my pocket, and I forgot about it again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they searched my coat, the pockets for anything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Maybe I had some gold, maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Yes, and when I came in, they took off my ring, my wedding ring, and my watch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Whatever I had with me, they took away from me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they did not-- the Chief of Gestapos that, that was there, but that, it's the SS men-- my coat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When I was tortured so many times, they just doubted if I'm Jewish or maybe not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They searched my coat, the coat which they took away from me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Everything, they took away from me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "In the pocket, they found the birth certificate from the church and the minister who gave it, not to me, but they thought to me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was given to the Polish woman whose home I stayed, who took my child from the hospital back, and she gave it to me, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So they found it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And as such, when, I lived as Wanda Grabowienska, the time that I lived during the war there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "When they got it, there was the signature of the church and the minister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't, never knew his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And to make sure that I'm the one, that I'm really Christian, they called him, not the minister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "First, they-- before the minister, sorry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Before they called him, they called in two men, interpreters, a Pole and a Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because I said that I was-- my father was Polish, my mother, Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That's why I spoke both languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They called a Pole and a Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
